# SECURITY-CRITICAL: never commit private key material
#
# The architect Ed25519 private key (architect_key.pem) lives locally
# only.  The public key portion is extracted to architect_pubkey.pem
# (safe to commit) and anchored cryptographically via the bridge-wallet
# attestation at eval/architect_key_attestation.json.
#
# Loss of architect_key.pem requires a key-rotation procedure
# (Procedure-VSD-K1 per VBDIP-0001 §5.1 strengthening A.5.5; defined in
# eval/PROCEDURES.md once Stream A.5 ships VSDIP-0003).

architect_key.pem
*.pem.key
*-key.pem

# Any private-key-shaped artifact must never enter git history
**/.*private*.pem
